	<p style="color: darkblue; font-size: 20pt"><b>UNIVERSITY</b><br/></p>
	<p style="font-size: 15pt">
	Grant University, was established in the year 1976 with a specific objective-
	<br /><br />"To establish and incorporate a teaching-come-affiliating University at California for the encouragement of
	interdisciplinary higher education and research with the special emphasis on studies of Life Sciences and Environmental
	and Eco_Science".During the last 26 years of its existence, the University has achieved a remarkable degree of success in its
	expansion programs, development and academic excellence.
	<br /><br />There are 66 boards of studies for developing and designing courses in different disciplines.
	<br /><br />In addition to the main campus, there are two satellites campus - Regional Center running post-graduate teaching at 
	California and National Law college at Texas.
